Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,下礼拜的烟火大会 大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,当然还有春辉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,跟春辉同学看烟火...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,美樱说要去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,美樱真是的 说什么没在跟春辉交往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么看他们都是互相喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,要让他们约会 在一起才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在正在念书
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 看烟火当然也有加优一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢那种人挤人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那我找别人好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,决定了 就跟那个人开心的玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不过好像很好玩 其实也是挺想去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,既然决定了就得准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}念书加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}阿姨 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法专心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,会太紧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,春辉同学会说什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,希望他会觉得我可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,等盂兰盆节过完 就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,去跟救美樱的那个人打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对方有联络过我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,说是应该可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,应该可以什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没有忘记东西吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,该出门了吧 拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要注意安全哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我就说甚平装穿起来舒服比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}刚才在家里也...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你们两个会一起?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚在那碰个正着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's Go
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,能见到那位恩人了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 盂兰盆节之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎样的人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,超期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,为什小夏会期待呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因为因为 不是很浪漫吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对方见到美樱一定也会非常开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果会就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,当然会了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你保证
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不可以乱跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,来 啊 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,美樱喜欢这种的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:12:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,优他们?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,没接
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,也没有已读
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法了 我们两个自己逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,气氛很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样快点交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,小灯好可爱 真的是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真好 要不要跟她说话呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不 做不到做不到做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我实在太没骨气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,走了啦 夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,让那两个人自己去吧 顺其自然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是肚子饿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我请你吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那我要...烤香肠 烤鱿鱼 奶油土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,还有巧克力香蕉 冰糖葫芦 棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想让我破产吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 快点来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不等你们咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,美樱 你还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有点热
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,美樱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,美樱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我买冷饮来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 烟火都开始放了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我也想休息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,恩人...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才不是在跟夏树说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前受一个人帮助过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一直很想跟他道谢 但都没有机会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,现在终于能见到那个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人是男生吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,玉屋~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs56}原本是放烟火的商行, 因为曾经与另一家烟火商竞演, 民众会在烟火升空时喊烟火商的名号来支持双方, 演变成现今看烟火的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 玉屋是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道还喊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,从这里看不到耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,春辉同学 你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里休息就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,难得都来看烟火了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 自己看也没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,画画还顺利吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我还在犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...我很期待你的画
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,美樱不是说过没办法面对镜头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果是画
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 这是电影社最后一部电影了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是集大成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的话 我希望美樱也能参与其中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.08,0:18:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,恋爱的颜色 大概不止一种
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管不顺利时 会变得像黑色夜幕一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但只要一点点转变 心情就会无比高昂 产生许多色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,世界就变得万般绚烂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就好比烟火一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,10公分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,若是能比10公分更加靠近...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 我去买些吃的...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,美樱...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,恋爱是烟火的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉能画出恋爱的画了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:19:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,救了我的那个人是怎样的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,会不顾危险 舍身去救位素未谋面的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是谁都办得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好感谢他才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能帮我拿着花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,救了美樱的那个人啊 就长眠在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好像本来身体就不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啊 美樱不需要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对方父母也这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,介意是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,芹泽...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,忘了带火柴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我去刚那家店买一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,明智老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,合田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,老师怎么会来这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,来替朋友扫墓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,芹泽千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.13,0:21:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,春辉的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:58.10,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10}「ねぇこっちおいでよ...なんて」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.40,0:22:05.42,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\be10}「えーっと、聞こえてますよ...なんて」
